Working in ECLIPSE........
first create a java project named as lucene_hotel_project
In this create a package as tourismsearchengine ,inside this create main.java
crete another package tourismsearchengine.database , Inside this create hotel.java and hoteltourismdatabase.java
create another package tourismsearchengine.search ,inside this create indexer.java and searching.java

lucene_hotel_project right click on this and configure build path and 
add external jars---->lucene-analyzers-common-8.11.1
------->lucene-core-8.11.1
------->lucene-queryparser-8.11.1

then apply and close.




